TopicTitle: Kerbal Space Program is crashing after loading up.

Articles.Content: Hello! So today after playing around in tundra exploration in stock with version 1.9.1 I decided to go back to 1.8.1 and reinstall every single mod I had ( got backups for them) for for some reason ksp decided to crash after loading everything in, the second attempt my screen blacked out and third it just crashed again. Any help would be appreciated, thank you! KSP Log: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Y98SUL0uXaTypO2dSBkmCLVx9t-xBNW6/view?usp=sharing

That log just cuts out in the middle of a line, no obvious errors before that so it could be a resource issue (running out of RAM) or you just need to leave it running for longer to let it load.

A mod list would help, as would the more detailed Player.log found at C:/Users/your username here/AppData/LocalLow/Squad/Kerbal Space Program
